This Software is provided as a research and educational tool for pharmaceutical
business-development practitioners. The valuations, buyer matches, deal-term
suggestions and any other outputs produced by this Software are estimates
based on public comparable transactions and simplified financial models.

They DO NOT constitute investment advice, legal advice, financial advice, or
solicitation to buy or sell securities. Real-world transactions involve
diligence, negotiation, market dynamics and human judgement that no model can
fully capture. Users are solely responsible for any decisions made based on
the outputs of this Software.

